https://ahcproject.netlify.app/

<!-- Apple Homepage Clone -->

This project is a minimalistic clone of the Apple homepage, designed using HTML and CSS. The focus is on clean design, responsiveness, and structured layout, mimicking Apple's sleek aesthetics.

<!-- Features -->

-Navigation Bar: Includes Apple logo, product categories, search, and shopping cart icons.

-Product Sections: Displays key Apple products with promotional content:
iPhone 14 – Highlights new features and availability.
iPhone 14 Pro – Showcases advanced capabilities.
Apple Watch Series 8 – Features promotional tagline and image.

-Typography & Colors:
Uses the Roboto font for a modern look.
Dark-themed sections with contrasting light text for readability.

Hover Effects: Navigation links change color on hover.

<!-- Technologies Used  -->

-HTML5: Structured layout and semantic elements.

-CSS3: Custom styling with:
Flexbox-based layout.
Color contrast for readability.
Consistent typography.
